&lt;html lang="en"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;
    &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Card&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;style&gt;
	 * {
	      -webkit-user-select: none;
	      user-select: none;
	  }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui;
            margin: 19px 20px 0 20px;
            background-color: #888;
            color: #fff;
        }
        #wrapper {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100px;
        }
        #applecard {
            width: 2956px;
            height: 1852px;
            color: rgb(127, 127, 127);
            line-height: 1;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 90px
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .typo {
            position: absolute;
            margin: 1110px 200px 0 177px;
            width: 1770px;
            z-index: 1
        }
        .cardholder {
            font-size: 127px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.07em;
        }
        .card {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        h4 {
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        button {
            color: #000;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 13px 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, .075);
            top: 20px;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .finalcard {
        	width: 100%;     
        	height: auto;   
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
          body {
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            color: #FFF;
          } 
          h5 {
            color: #1E1E1E;
            background-color: #FFF;
          }
        }
    &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
    &lt;div id="wrapper"&gt;
    &lt;div&gt;&lt;button class="button" onClick="createcard()"&gt;Generate your Card&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div id="applecard"&gt;
            &lt;div class="typo"&gt;
                &lt;h1 class="cardholder"&gt;￼&lt;/h1&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class="card"&gt;
                &lt;img src="data:image/png;base64,"&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script&gt;￼&lt;/script&gt;

    var applecard = document.querySelector("#applecard");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

        html2canvas(applecard, {

                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");

                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your Card has been generated.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: #444"&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalcard" src="'+img+'"/&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            },
            letterRendering: true
        })
    }
    &lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
